data.meta_description: Governor Nelson Rockefeller (New York) comes to Columbia during the Republican primary season. Rockefeller is greeted at the airport by Columbia mayor Lester Bates, prominent S. C. Republican party member J. Drake Edens, Jr., and reporters and supporters. Press conference. Rockefeller observes that candidates should be appealing nationally, not just regionally.
